Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same color as your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I felt when I saw this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Major Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in the hospital\Nfor 120 days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My strength has almost recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Movement is still a little difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can perform my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me return to my post soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,KINGDOM OF ENCIEL\NSOMEWHERE IN THE CAPITAL OF ENCHAINE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Her existence\Nwas hidden from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However, people who knew about her\Nsaid that she was a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She would fight if you ordered her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She just looked like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just a tool...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,without a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel Hodgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the major?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Major Gilbert?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he return home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How are his injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,His injuries were severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the major...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:03:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They've given us permission to\Ndischarge you from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel Hodgins came all this way\Nto pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Lt. Colonel Hodgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten you were a Lt. Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways. So, you do remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met twice. Once during training\Nand the night before the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was writing a report to Major Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that writing words\Nwould be good for my recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the major well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that means he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor told me that we won the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What post is he assigned to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When shall I join him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get changed first. I'll have them\Nsend the car in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,These finally arrived.\NThey're your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they mistakenly delivered it\Nto an army base far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The emerald brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is everything from the garrison\Nand the place where they found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go look for it if it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The major gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-You must...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,These are his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When will I receive the next order\Nfrom the major?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm limited to only performing certain\Nduties because of my current condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Congratulations\Non getting discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what you'd like, so,\NI bought three. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You have to choose one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend that the world is about to end.\NOkay. Three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... the puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The major's brother once told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're Gilbert's dog."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The train tracks around here\Nwere damaged during the bombing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and aren't usable anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been to Leiden before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,From the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is. The port of Leiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,LEIDEN, THE CAPITAL OF\NLEIDENSCHAFTLICH
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert was thinking about\Nyour future after the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to leave you\Nwith the Evergarden household,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,his most trusted relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I contacted them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the couple said they'd be happy\Nto take you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the lady of the\NEvergarden household.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A bow would suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it take around three days\Nfrom Enchaine now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Normally, I'd be able\Nto return in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But the war has been going on\Nfor four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to take some more time\Nto restore everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry. Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! You'll get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem. I can't feel heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But your bandages...\NQuick, we have to cool them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oliver, bring some ice!\N-Yes, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These arms are made of adamant silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a bit bulky, but they're sturdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not accustomed to them yet.\NI should be able to adjust soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come this way for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I used these when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice. Try them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to Tiffany, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of me as your real mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me anything. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have parents, so,\NI don't need any replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a son,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but he was killed in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't become a replacement\Nfor your lost child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Gilbert's wish\Nis for you to happily live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The major.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The major. Why is he leaving me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I lost my arms,\Nand lost my value as a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just trained a little,\NI could still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. The war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the major's tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he doesn't need me anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then I should be thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw me away somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel Hodgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the army.\NI'm not a Lt. Colonel anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me "President."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought an old house\Nand renovated it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The first floor is the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. Please write the receiver's\Nand sender's address on this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow three days for delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The second floor houses the office\Nand the writing department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This department writes letters\Nat the requests of our clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still many people\Nwho don't know how to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how to write either\Nuntil the major taught me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about starting\Na business once the war ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The government's postal service\Ndoesn't address the civilian's needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so, I thought it would be\Na good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an order for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert left you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm giving you orders instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can work. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Benedict.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to say\N"How can I help you, President?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's up with you?\N-You did that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Benedict. He's a postman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an old friend\Nfrom before I started this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Benedict, this is Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to work here\Nas a postman, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's highly capable\Nof performing her duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach her what she needs to know, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your stuff here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uniform. Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! H... Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better to take those off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it hard to sort the mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort them just like it says here.\NPut them in those shelves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a huge pile of mail,\Nbut no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The break room is on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've almost completed my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you working the whole time?\NWithout taking a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to long hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, do you want to try\Ndelivering the mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Delivering?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You deliver the letter\Nto the address that's written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"We will discuss financing\Nafter reviewing your performance." Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like some companies\Ndo nighttime deliveries, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm delivering the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, mail delivery was meant for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And make sure to take breaks during work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-You just got released from the hospital.\N-It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the office\Nonce you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have space in the attic,\Nbut you can sleep there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, the Evergarden household\Nhas agreed to take you in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,until you become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like leaving you\Nat the mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there was a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to put it nicely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How was I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the last order\Nyou received from Gilbert?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "Run away and live freely."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in the army\Never since you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've spent your life\Nfulfilling your duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to learn a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it might be easier to keep living
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if you didn't learn them,\Nif you didn't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't realize\Nthat your body is on fire
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and burning up\Nbecause of the things you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not. You don't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You are burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you like that, but left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why when Gilbert\Nleft you with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this was my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'll realize for the first time\Nthat you have many burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Miss Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you\Nto write something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Write something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I don't know how to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you write a letter for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I write?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to talk about it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that my childhood friend\Nin the countryside
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,received a marriage offer\Nfrom another man. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"You were the first person
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,who was kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have done anything for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to know what you're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to understand\Nwhat's in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we're apart now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to reception on the first floor\Nfor the delivery process.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for using\Nthe Auto Memory Doll Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nthat the man just now wanted to say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to work as an Auto Memory Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's still hard for me to hold a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can operate a typewriter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask why\Nyou want to do this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what it means!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The major said those words to me\Nafter he gave me my last orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time\NI heard those words from the major.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,people become Auto Memory Dolls\Nbecause they understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She had always just followed\NGilbert's orders in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time\Nshe asserted her own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone said she didn't have a heart\Nand that she was a tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but she said, "I want to know\Nwhat 'I love you' means."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.37,0:23:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! There's no way\NI'm going to let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.86,0:23:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Live, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,From the bottom of my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by\NHoday Stearns
